Noda Calls Tobacco Tax Hike ‘Option’ for Rebuilding, Asahi Says

-- B y   M o n a m i   Y u i
-- 
2011-09-24T01:45:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-24/noda-calls-tobacco-tax-hike-option-for-rebuilding-asahi-says.html
Japanese Prime Minister  Yoshihiko
Noda  is considering an increase of tobacco taxes as one
“option” to fund reconstruction from the March 11 natural
disasters, the Asahi newspaper reported today, citing comments
by Noda.   Speaking to reporters Sept. 22 in  New York , Noda also said
he aims to submit a third extra budget to the Diet in October,
suggesting he will accelerate discussions with opposition
parties, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Monami Yui in Tokyo at 
 myui1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
